Trinity::

She walked over to Nightlight."yeah, that's right. You never told me 
your name. Well, Mine name is Trinity. So what's your's huh?" She 
looked up at Nightlight. "And don't worry. I'll protect you."

Trinity never took into account that all the other bots were 6 times 
her size. She just stood guard infront of Nightlight and growled and 
paced, trying her best to look fearce and menacing.
